Wpf.TreeViewExtension
=====================
Extensions of WPF(Windows Presentation Foundation) controls, TreeView and TreeViewItem.

 * ITreeViewItemVisitor interface
   Scans all TreeViewItem controls in TreeView, or a TreeViewItem controls and all children of it.
 
 * TreeView.SelectItemFromHeader method
   Select a TreeViewItem by programmatically.
   The parameter header is the object contained in the TreeViewItem to select.